<strong>Ebony Bladed Sword</strong>
<font size=-1>(<a href="/prices/item/ebony_bladed_sword.shtml">View Going Price</a>)</font><BR>
Skill: <a href="/weapons/1h_slash.shtml">1H Slash</a><BR>
Damage per second - 6.25<BR>
Damage 7 - Delay 24<BR>
Weight: 2.0 - HEF, HUM, ELF<BR>
Classes: <a href="/ranger/weapons/1h_slash.shtml">RNG</a><BR>
Effect: <a href="http://www.maximumeq.com/spells/individual/ensnaring_roots.shtml?spellID=401">Ensnaring Roots</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) <BR>
</font>
Dropped in Lower Guk by Minotaur Patriarch.<BR>
<BR>
Avg. Price Overall: 740pp (66 quotes)<BR>
Last 30 Days: 400pp (1 quotes)<BR>

