<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Arbok Ekans</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-01-15 15:07:42</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>That's not true, when the evony blade procs, snare is canceled out<BR>
until the effect is gone.  Reason is because the effect: Ensaring Roots<BR>
is a "Root" spell and overrides snare which is a lesser form of<BR>
root.  If you tried, you would get a "That spell effect does not hold"<BR>
etc etc.<BR>
<BR>
Ensaring Roots does 47 damage(at lvl.37) and roots for about...10-20<BR>
seconds.  An experienced ranger would know to snare at the right time<BR>
for maximum effect.  As for the proc, I'm not exactly sure when it starts<BR>
because I received this beautiful rather late.  It could be lvl.30 tho.<BR>
</font></td></tr></table>
