<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I have an EBS, and I love it! However most of the groups I hunt with tell me one thing beofre we enter a dungeon, "dump that POS weapon and use your Short Sword of Morin". My other weapon is a runed falchion, so I still can dish out damage so it doesnt really bother me too much. But from my experience most higher level ppl will tell you to lose the EBS in a dungeon setting. True, it requires a different fighting style, but most ppl dont want to adjust. I just wish Verant could fix the weapon, because I truly do love it!</font></td></tr></table>
